dataList.title: Tieqiu Crew
dataList.content: D’you fellers have any idea what you’ve just walked into?

dataList.title: Tieqiu Crew
dataList.content: Try mucking about and we’ll make the most acrobatic poses known to man outta you.

dataList.title: Tieqiu Crew
dataList.content: Then we’ll lop off your digits joint by joint and make purdy mahjong tiles with ‘em.
Sheesh… Some warm welcome that was.
Feh, I’m not one to let introductions like that go unanswered. Oi! Dust up!
